 font-size: 12pt;\">Th\u00ed sinh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 trung c\u1ea5p c\u00f9ng nh\u00f3m ng\u00e0nh d\u1ef1 tuy\u1ec3n<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><strong><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">2.\u00a0\u00a0 Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c tuy\u1ec3n sinh<\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">X\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u1ecdc b\u1ea1 THPT: T\u1ed5ng \u0111i\u1ec3m trung b\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a 05 h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 (L\u1edbp 10, L\u1edbp 11, K\u1ef3 I l\u1edbp 12) ho\u1eb7c n\u0103m l\u1edbp 12 c\u1ee7a 03 m\u00f4n trong t\u1ed5 h\u1ee3p x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n + \u0111i\u1ec3m \u01b0u ti\u00ean (n\u1ebfu c\u00f3) \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1eeb 15 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><strong><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">3.\u00a0\u00a0 Th\u1eddi gian<\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><em>Nh\u1eadn h\u1ed3 s\u01a1: <\/em>T\u1eeb ng\u00e0y <strong>04\/12\/2023 <\/strong>\u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y <strong>25\/12\/2023.<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><em>X\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n: <\/em>Ng\u00e0y <strong>26\/12\/2023<\/strong>.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><em>Nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc<\/em>: T\u1eeb ng\u00e0y <strong>29\/12\/2023 <\/strong>\u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y <strong>30\/12\/2023<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><strong><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">4.\u00a0\u00a0 Ng\u00e0nh tuy\u1ec3n sinh, th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o, h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c h\u1ecdc<\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><em>Ng\u00e0nh tuy\u1ec3n sinh<\/em><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: middle;\" width=\"68\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>TT<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"