"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">T\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p THPT: 4 n\u0103m<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">T\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p Trung h\u1ecdc chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, Trung c\u1ea5p chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p: 2,5 &#8211; 3 n\u0103m<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">T\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p Cao \u0111\u1eb3ng tr\u1edf l\u00ean: 1,5 n\u0103m<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><em>H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c h\u1ecdc: 100% h\u1ecdc online<\/em><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Sau khi ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc, sinh vi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 c\u1ea5p b\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o ch\u00ednh quy <em>(Tr\u00ean v\u0103n b\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng ghi h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o)<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><em>Thi k\u1ebft th\u00fac h\u1ecdc ph\u1ea7n sinh vi\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn 1 trong 3 \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m sau<\/em>:<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Mi\u1ec1n B\u1eafc: Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4, Km 15, Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ed9 32, Kim Chung, Ho\u00e0i \u0110\u1ee9c, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Mi\u1ec1n Trung: Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0 L\u1ea1t &#8211; S\u1ed1 1, Ph\u00f9 \u0110\u1ed5ng Thi\u00ean V\u01b0\u01a1ng, Ph\u01b0\u1eddng 8, TP. \u0110\u00e0 L\u1ea1t, L\u00e2m \u0110\u1ed3ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Mi\u1ec1n Nam: Tr\u01b0\u1eddng Cao \u0111\u